divs: Sighting DetailsGoing to work saw this diamond in the sky from a distance then i got out of my car to go into work as i was going into work the object must of saw me it came closer and it came closer then it flew right over me it sounded like almost like a plane but it was much quieter i kid you not it looked like the millennium falcon from star wars i thought i was dreaming... so i went back after a hour outside and looked both direction the place the object came from and the place i saw it leave the crazy thing is the place i first saw this object it seemed to come from some sort of portal because there was a spot in the sky that was illuminated in the place i first saw it from a distance now the next day there is a spotlight in the area where i saw this object first come from ...
